=================================
INSTALL for gpulib IDL package
=================================

This file describes how to install the gpulib IDL package.  
Here is a short summary:

1. Install CUDA
2. Install gpulib
3. point your IDL_DLM_PATH to the location of the gpulib.dlm file.
4. point your IDL_PATH to the location of gpuinit.pro

If you just want to use gpulib in the IDL emulation mode, you only need
to do step 4.

Building of gpulib

Linux: 
./configure ; make 

Windows:
build_win





